@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

|Online System| as OS
|Data Platform| as DP
|Evaluation Data| as ED
|Model Iteration| as MI
|New Model| as NM

rectangle "Evaluation Closed Loop" as ECL {
  OS -> DP: User Behavior Data
  DP -> ED: Data Processing
  ED -> MI: Evaluation Dataset
  MI -> NM: Model Training
  NM -> OS: Deployment
  
  OS -[dashed]-> DP: A/B Testing Feedback
  DP -[dashed]-> ED: Data Updates
  ED -[dashed]-> MI: Effect Analysis
  MI -[dashed]-> OS: Continuous Improvement
}

note right of ECL
  Data-model co-evolution
  cycle for continuous
  system improvement
end note

@enduml
